{"url": "https://www.ics.uci.edu/~mopy/misc.html", "content": "\n<!--\n/*\n *\n *  File: misc.html\n *  Created by Shivajit Mohapatra\n *  Date: Jan 15, 2013\n *\n * Copyright (c) 2012 Shivajit Mohapatra\n * All rights reserved.\n *\n */\n-->\n\n<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"utf-8\">\n    <title>Shivajit Mohapatra :: Miscellanea</title>\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\"/>\n    <meta name=\"description\" content=\"Home page of Shivajit Mohapatra\"/>\n    <meta name=\"author\" content=\"Shivajit Mohapatra\"/>\n    <meta name=\"keywords\" content=\"Motorola, UCI, Shivajit Mohapatra, mopy,\"/>\n    <meta http-equiv=\"content-type\" content=\"text/html; charset=utf-8\"/>\n    <link rel=\"shortcut icon\" href=\"images/favicon.ico\" type=\"image/x-icon\"/>\n\n    <!-- Le styles -->\n    <link href=\"css/bootstrap-responsive.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n    <link href=\"css/style.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n    <script src=\"js/jquery.js\"></script>\n    <link href=\"css/bootstrap.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n    <script src=\"js/bootstrap.js\"></script>\n    <script src=\"js/bootstrap-popover.js\"></script>\n\n    <style type=\"text/css\">\n        body {\n            padding-top: 30px;\n            padding-bottom: 40px;\n            padding-left: 35px;\n            padding-right: 35px;\n        }\n\n        .sidebar-nav {\n            padding: 9px 0;\n        }\n    </style>\n\n\n\n    <script>\n        var message = 'Currently offline. Kindly email me for a copy!';\n\n        $(document).ready(function() {\n            $(function () {\n                $(\"#shortres , #longres, #cover, #statements\").popover({\n                    trigger: 'hover',\n                    placement: 'top' ,\n                    offset: 1,\n                    content: message\n                });\n            })\n\n        });\n    </script>\n\n</head>\n\n<!-- Body start  -->\n<body>\n\n<table id=\"content\" width=\"900\" border=\"0\" align=\"center\">\n    <tbody>\n    <tr>\n        <td>\n            <!-- Header Navigation -->\n            <div class=\"navbar navbar-static\">\n                <div class=\"navbar-inner\">\n                    <div class=\"container\">\n                        <div class=\"nav-collapse collapse \">\n                            <ul class=\"nav\">\n                                <li class=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"./index.html\">Bio</a>\n                                </li>\n                                <li class=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"./portfolio.html\">Portfolio</a>\n                                </li>\n                                <li class=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"./publications.html\">Publications</a>\n                                </li>\n                                <li class=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"./teaching.html\">Engagements</a>\n                                </li>\n                                <li class=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"./personal.html\">Personal</a>\n                                </li>\n                                <li class=\"active\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\">Miscellanea</a>\n                                </li>\n                            </ul>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <!-- End Header Navigation -->\n\n            <!-- ----------------------S N I P   B E L O W---------------------------------- -->\n\n            <!-- Resume   -->\n            <div id=\"service\">\n\n            <br/><br/><p class=\"paraHeader clear\"> :: Resume </p>\n            <hr size=\"2\" color=\"#000\" width=\"95%\" />\n\n            <p>\n                Available upon request. Please send me a note if you need my resume or statements.\n                <ul>\n                    <li>Resume (<a href=\"#\" id=\"shortres\" rel=\"popover\">short</a> ,\n                        <a href=\"#\" id=\"longres\" rel=\"popover\">long</a>)</li>\n                    <li><a href=\"\" id=\"cover\" rel=\"popover\">Cover Letter</a></li>\n                    <li><a href=\"\" id=\"statements\" rel=\"popover\">Statements</a></li>\n                </ul>\n\n            </p>\n\n                        <!-- xxx  -->\n    \n            <br /><br />\n\n                <p class=\"paraHeader\"> :: Frequently Asked Questions </p>\n                <hr size=\"2\" color=\"#000\" width=\"95%\" />\n\n                 <p>\n                   <strong>Q.</strong> <em>So what's happening at Motorola labs with the Google acquisition and all?</em> <br />\n                   <strong>A.</strong> Unfortunately, Google\n                     recently <a href=\"http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-12-19/google-sells-motorola-home-to-arris-for-2-35-billion-correct-.html\">sold</a>\n                     the Motorola Home division to Arris.\n                     Motorola labs which has traditionally been funded by the Home business unit will now become\n                     part of Arris.\n                </p>\n                 <br />\n                <p>\n                   <strong>Q.</strong> <em>I want to get an internship / full-time position at Motorola Research.\n                    Can you help?</em> <br />\n                   <strong>A.</strong> Currently, Motorola labs has a complete hiring freeze. So I will not be able to\n                    help with internships or full-time positions.\n                </p>\n                 <br />\n                <p >\n                   <strong>Q.</strong> <em>You and your team have produced so many interesting applications. Why are\n                    they not on the app store(s)?</em><br />\n                   <strong>A.</strong> Much of the work we have done in the research labs have been prototypes\n                    for internal show and tell. Again, many of the concepts and ideas are published in journals\n                    and patent disclosures. If we had the resources, much of our creations could have been products\n                    on the app stores. But sadly, we have had fewer and fewer resources over the years. However,\n                    some of the prototypes we have worked on are well on their way to becoming products in some\n                    form or the other.\n                </p>\n\n\n                                <!-- Travel  -->\n\n                <br/><br/><p class=\"paraHeader clear\"> :: Links </p>\n                <hr size=\"2\" color=\"#000\" width=\"95%\" />\n\n                <ul>\n                    <li><a href=\"http://www.psychologytoday.com/\">Psychology Today</a> (One of my favorites.)</li>\n                </ul>\n\n                            <!-- xxx  -->\n\n\n            </div>\n        </td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n        <td>\n            <!-- Footer -->\n            <div class=\"footer\">\n                <div id=\"copyright\">&copy;<small>Shivajit Mohapatra</small>\n                    <br/>\n                    <small>Designed with Twitter Bootstrap</small>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </td>\n    </tr>\n    </tbody>\n</table>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n", "encoding": "ascii"}